(71, '', 0, 'bootstrap相关', NULL, '', '<p>--role:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>使用role属性告诉辅助设备（如屏幕阅读器）这个元素所扮演的角色，属于<a class="wrap external" href="http://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.zhangxinxu.com/wordpress/%3Fp%3D2277" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank">WAI-ARIA</a>. 例如点击的按钮，就是role=&quot;button&quot;；会让这个元素可点击；</p>\r\n\r\n<p>本质上是增强语义性，当现有的HTML标签不能充分表达语义性的时候，就可以借助role来说明。通常这种情况出现在一些自定义的组件上（例如一个tree组件，html里目前还没有tree这个标签），这样可增强组件的可访问性、可用性和可交互性。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--<code>sr-only（BS）</code></p>\r\n\r\n<p>如果你使用图标是为了表达某些含义（不仅仅是为了装饰用），请确保你所要表达的意思能够通过被辅助设备识别，例如，包含额外的内容并通过 <code>.sr-only</code> 类让其在视觉上表现出隐藏的效果。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--<code>.container</code> 类用于固定宽度并支持响应式布局的容器。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--<code>.container-fluid</code> 类用于 100% 宽度，占据全部视口（viewport）的容器。</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>affix.js</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nalert.js<br />\r\n&nbsp; http://www.cnblogs.com/wumadi/p/3272614.html</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nbutton.js<br />\r\nhttp://www.softwhy.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=8710</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\ncarousel.js<br />\r\n&nbsp; http://www.cnblogs.com/wumadi/p/3274874.html</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\ncollapse.js<br />\r\n&nbsp; http://www.cnblogs.com/wumadi/p/3274402.html</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\ndropdown.js<br />\r\nhttp://www.open-open.com/lib/view/open1436603216973.html</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nmodal.js<br />\r\nhttp://www.oschina.net/code/snippet_181985_39014</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\npopover.js<br />\r\n&nbsp; http://www.cnblogs.com/wumadi/p/3272319.html</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nscrollspy.js<br />\r\n&nbsp; http://www.cnblogs.com/wumadi/p/3270183.html</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\ntab.js<br />\r\n&nbsp; http://www.cnblogs.com/wumadi/p/3270528.html</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\ntooltip.js<br />\r\n&nbsp; http://www.cnblogs.com/wumadi/p/3272200.html</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\ntransition.js<br />\r\nhttp://www.tuicool.com/articles/EfYjq2J</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>bs dorpDown<br />\r\nhttp://blog.csdn.net/learninginjava/article/details/49231091<br />\r\nhttp://schifred.iteye.com/blog/2267763</p>\r\n\r\n<p>bootstrap 源码分析：<br />\r\nhttp://www.tuicool.com/articles/NNZNzi<br />\r\nhttp://www.softwhy.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=8710<br />\r\nhttp://suqing.iteye.com/blog/1984131</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>BS源码：<br />\r\nhttp://my.oschina.net/lyzg/blog?catalog=3307850<br />\r\nhttp://www.open-open.com/lib/tag/Bootstrap<br />\r\nhttp://www.tuicool.com/articles/NNZNzi &nbsp; button.js</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>BS源码分析：<br />\r\nhttp://www.oschina.net/search?q=bootstrap%E6%BA%90%E7%A0%81&amp;scope=blog&amp;fromerr=m4NXeUoN</p>\r\n\r\n<p>modal.js:<br />\r\nhttp://my.oschina.net/lyzg/blog/494815</p>\r\n\r\n<p>transition.js:<br />\r\nhttp://my.oschina.net/lyzg/blog/423631?fromerr=oLvpxqmD</p>\r\n\r\n<p>dropdown.js:<br />\r\nhttp://my.oschina.net/lyzg/blog/476787</p>\r\n\r\n<p>tab.js:<br />\r\nhttp://my.oschina.net/lyzg/blog/469210</p>\r\n\r\n<p>alert.js:<br />\r\nhttp://my.oschina.net/lyzg/blog/423651</p>\r\n\r\n<p>button.js:<br />\r\nhttp://my.oschina.net/lyzg/blog/469208</p>\r\n', '2016-08-23 02:01:31', '2017-03-18 00:19:31', 26, 0, ''),
(72, '', 0, 'wampService相关', NULL, '', '<p style="line-height:16px;">WampServer2.1e-x32.exe:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">修改端口：<span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">E:wamp/bin/apache/Apache2.4.9/conf下的httpd.conf</span>修改：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height: 16px; margin-left: 40px;">Listen 80 【约46行】</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height: 16px; margin-left: 40px;">ServerName localhost:80 【约171行】</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">使其可以用公网ip访问：...httpd.conf：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; Deny from all 【约233行】<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; Allow from 127.0.0.1</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">改成如下：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="line-height: 16px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Allow from all</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">修改phpmyadmin(数据库界面)账号密码以使其与MySQL一致：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height: 16px; margin-left: 40px;">apps/phpmyadmin4.1.14/config.inc.php修改[&#39;password&#39;]=&#39;新密码&#39;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>家wamp手机不能访问非80端口ip地址？</p>\r\n\r\n<p>对比家中和公司wamp配置区别？</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>wamp修改根目录：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1--&ldquo;script&rdquo;文件夹的config.inc.php：&ldquo;$wwwDir&nbsp;=&nbsp;$c_installDir.&#39;/www&#39;;&rdquo;改成如改成D:website</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2--如：E:wamp/bin/apache/Apache2.4.9/conf下的httpd.conf：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>改 - DocumentRoot：&ldquo;c:/wamp/www/&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>改 - &lt;Directory &quot;c:/wamp/www/&quot;&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>虚拟主机设置：<a href="http://www.cnblogs.com/hi-bazinga/archive/2012/04/23/2466605.html" target="_blank">http://www.cnblogs.com/hi-bazinga/archive/2012/04/23/2466605.html</a></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>让虚拟主机可以列举文件夹目录：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">-配置文件httpd.conf如下：（约190行）</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">Options&nbsp;FollowSymLinks</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">改成：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">Options Indexes FollowSymLinks</span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>mac的mamp配置虚拟主机：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">Hosts &nbsp;-》 左下角&lsquo;+&rsquo;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">General - 设置 Server name 和 Document root等</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">Extended - 勾选 Indexes （为了有权限列举目录）</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>mamp浏览目录支持中文文件名：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">http://blog.csdn.net/zhuizhuziwo/article/details/8016018 （测试无效？）</p>\r\n', '2016-08-24 01:42:53', '2017-03-21 01:57:48', 25, 0, ''),
(73, '', 0, 'js静态模板', NULL, '', '<p>var data = {<br />\r\n&nbsp; people1: [<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; {first:&quot;Jeff1&quot;,last: &quot;Adams1&quot;},<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; {first:&quot;Eugenia1&quot;,last: &quot;Tyzak1&quot;}<br />\r\n&nbsp; ],<br />\r\n&nbsp; people2: [<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; {first:&quot;Jeff2&quot;,last: &quot;Adams2&quot;},<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; {first:&quot;Eugenia2&quot;,last: &quot;Tyzak2&quot;}<br />\r\n&nbsp; ]<br />\r\n};</p>\r\n\r\n<p>$.templates({<br />\r\n&nbsp; peopleTmpl: &quot;#peopleTemplate&quot;<br />\r\n});</p>\r\n\r\n<p>$.templates.peopleTmpl.link(&quot;#people&quot;, data);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>循环数组：</p>\r\n\r\n<pre style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; list-style-image: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 21.6px; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important;">\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5 !important;">var  peoples = {names: [&quot;Maradona&quot;,&quot;Pele&quot;,&quot;Ronaldo&quot;,&quot;Messi&quot;]}</span>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n<pre style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; list-style-image: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 21.6px; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important;">\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5 !important;">{{for names}}\r\n  </span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5 !important;">&lt;</span><span style="color: rgb(128, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5 !important;">div</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5 !important;">&gt;</span>\r\n    <span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5 !important;">&lt;</span><span style="color: rgb(128, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5 !important;">b</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5 !important;">&gt;</span>{{: #index+1}}.<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5 !important;">&lt;/</span><span style="color: rgb(128, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5 !important;">b</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5 !important;">&gt;</span>\r\n    <span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5 !important;">&lt;</span><span style="color: rgb(128, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5 !important;">span</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5 !important;">&gt;</span>{{: #data}}<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5 !important;">&lt;/</span><span style="color: rgb(128, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5 !important;">span</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5 !important;">&gt;</span>\r\n  <span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5 !important;">&lt;/</span><span style="color: rgb(128, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5 !important;">div</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5 !important;">&gt;</span><span style="line-height: 1.5 !important;">\r\n{{/for}}</span></pre>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>最简单的前端模板引擎:http://www.cnblogs.com/dolphinX/p/3489269.html</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-family: Consolas, &quot;Bitstream Vera Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">yaya-template:</span>http://www.uloveit.com.cn/template/</p>\r\n\r\n<p>{$...$}：内部是html,外部可执行js脚本</p>\r\n\r\n<p>{%...%}：内部是变量</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color:#F0FFF0;">for (var i=0; i&lt;data.length; i++){</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#F0FFF0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;{$&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#F0FFF0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#F0FFF0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;h4&gt;{% data[i].xx&nbsp;%}&lt;/h4&gt;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#F0FFF0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$}&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#F0FFF0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;if(data[i].aaa== 1){</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#F0FFF0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;{$ &lt;figure class=&quot;green&quot;&gt;111&lt;/figure&gt; $}</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#F0FFF0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;}</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#F0FFF0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;if(data[i].aaa== 2){</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#F0FFF0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;{$ &lt;figure class=&quot;yellow&quot;&gt;222&lt;/figure&gt; $}</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#F0FFF0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;}</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#F0FFF0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;{$</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#F0FFF0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#F0FFF0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$}</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#F0FFF0;">}</span></p>\r\n', '2016-09-07 01:22:21', '2017-12-29 21:40:51', 94, 0, ''),
