(93, '', 0, '谷歌调试', NULL, '', '<p>谷歌Chrome Developer Tools浅析：<a href="http://www.kuqin.com/developtool/20120625/321085.html" target="_blank">http://www.kuqin.com/developtool/20120625/321085.html</a></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>网页翻译：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- 右击&lsquo;翻成English&rsquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- 拉到网页最下面以便让整个网页都翻译成英文（本网页tab切换的也切换一遍）</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- 审查元素 &#39;Elements&#39; html标签 - 右击 - Copy - Copy OuterHTML 就把翻译成英文的网页复制了下来</p>\r\n', '2017-11-07 08:12:05', '2019-07-25 12:40:02', 108, 0, '');
