(109, '', 0, '新API', NULL, '', '<p>--Canvas<br />\r\n--SVG<br />\r\n--Forms API<br />\r\n--拖动<br />\r\n--webStorage_(本地存储)<br />\r\n--web Workers_(线程)<br />\r\n--webSocket_(全双工实时通信)（套接字）<br />\r\n--离线web应用_(应用缓存)<br />\r\n--服务器推送<br />\r\n--Geolocation_(地理位置)<br />\r\n--Communication_(跨域通信)<br />\r\n--Web sql_(本地数据库)<br />\r\n--indexedDB<br />\r\n--历史记录管理<br />\r\n--文件系统api<br />\r\n--blob<br />\r\n--类型化数组和array buffer</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>教程：http://www.w3school.com.cn/html5/index.asp<br />\r\nHTML5(MDN文档)：https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/HTML5</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>正则表达式<br />\r\n数据列表元素<br />\r\n下载属性<br />\r\nDns的预先加载处理<br />\r\n链接网页的预先加载处理</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Media API<br />\r\nText Track API<br />\r\nApplication Cache API<br />\r\nUser Interaction<br />\r\nData Transfer API<br />\r\nCommand API<br />\r\nConstraint Validation API<br />\r\nHistory API</p>\r\n', '2016-11-22 03:06:27', '2018-12-26 17:55:08', 53, 0, ''),
(110, '', 1, 'DOCTYPE声明', NULL, '', '<p>在&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">HTML5</span>&nbsp;中只有一种声明类型：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="color: rgb(128, 0, 128);"><span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>在&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">HTML4</span>&nbsp;中有三种声明类型：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><strong><span style="color:#B22222;">HTML 4.01 Strict</span></strong> -- 文档严格定义类型：该 DTD 包含所有 HTML 元素和属性，但不包括装饰性的（比如 u、b等）和弃用的（比如 font）元素。不允许使用框架。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><br />\r\n<strong><span style="color:#B22222;">HTML 4.01 Transitional</span></strong> -- 文档过渡定义类型：该 DTD 包含所有 HTML 元素和属性，包括装饰性的（比如 u、b等）和弃用的（比如 font）元素。不允许使用框架。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd&quot;&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><br />\r\n<strong><span style="color:#B22222;">HTML 4.01 Frameset</span></strong> -- 文档框架定义类型：除 frameset 元素取代了 body 元素之外，该 DTD 等同于 HTML 4.01 Transitional，但允许使用框架。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Frameset//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/frameset.dtd&quot;&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\n<strong><span style="color:#B22222;">XHTML 1.0 Strict</span></strong> -- 必须以格式正确的 XML 来编写标记以外等同于HTML 4.01 Strict</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd&quot;&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><br />\r\n<span style="color:#B22222;"><strong>XHTML 1.0 Transitional</strong></span> -- 必须以格式正确的 XML 来编写标记以外等同于HTML 4.01 Transitional</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd&quot;&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><br />\r\n<strong><span style="color:#B22222;">XHTML 1.0 Frameset</span></strong> -- 该 DTD 等同于 XHTML 1.0 Transitional，但允许框架集内容。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Frameset//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-frameset.dtd&quot;&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><br />\r\n<strong><span style="color:#B22222;">XHTML 1.1</span></strong> -- 该 DTD 等同于 XHTML 1.0 Strict，但允许添加模型（例如提供对东亚语系的 ruby 支持）。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.1//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml11/DTD/xhtml11.dtd&quot;&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>HTML 元素和有效的 DTD：<a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/tags/html_ref_dtd.asp" target="_blank"><span style="color:#FFA07A;">http://www.w3school.com.cn/tags/html_ref_dtd.asp</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>DOCTYPE 中xhtml 1.0和 html 4.01区别：<a href="http://www.jb51.net/css/37839.html" target="_blank"><span style="color:#FFA07A;">http://www.jb51.net/css/37839.html</span></a></p>\r\n', '2016-11-22 03:08:34', '2018-12-26 17:19:51', 48, 0, ''),
(111, '', 8, 'meta元信息', NULL, '', '<p>meta属性介绍一：<a href="http://www.haorooms.com/post/html_meta_ds" target="_blank"><span style="color:#FFA07A;">http://www.haorooms.com/post/html_meta_ds</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>meta属性介绍二：<a href="http://blog.csdn.net/xiaoqijun/article/details/6318619" target="_blank"><span style="color:#FFA07A;">http://blog.csdn.net/xiaoqijun/article/details/6318619</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:#FF0000;">&lt;meta&gt;</span>元素是html语言头部的一个辅助性标签；提供有关页面的元信息（meta-information）。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">说明：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- 永远位于 head 元素内部；<br />\r\n- 在 HTML 中，&lt;meta&gt; 标签没有结束标签；在 XHTML 中，&lt;meta&gt; 标签必须被正确地关闭；</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- 元数据总是以<span style="color:#B22222;"><strong>名称/值</strong></span>的形式被成对传递的；</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">* 名称/值形式中的&#39;名称&#39;由属性&#39;http-equiv&#39;或&#39;name&#39;定义</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">* http-equiv属性：把 content 属性关联到 HTTP 头部。</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">* name属性：把 content 属性关联到一个名称。</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">* 名称/值形式中的&#39;值&#39;由属性&#39;content&#39;定义；属性&#39;content&#39;是必须的，定义与 http-equiv 或 name 属性相关的元信息</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">*&nbsp;其中还有一个可选的属性&#39;scheme&#39;，定义用于翻译 content 属性值的格式。</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong><span style="color:#B22222;">name属性：</span></strong>HTML 和 XHTML 标签都没有指定任何预先定义的 &lt;meta&gt; 名称。通常情况下，您可以自由使用对自己和源文档的读者来说富有意义的名称。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><strong>语法格式：</strong>&lt;meta name=&quot;参数&quot;content=&quot;具体的参数值&quot;&gt;。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><strong>常用参数</strong>如下：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">keywords：</span>用来告诉搜索引擎你网页的关键字。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta name=&quot;keywords&quot;content=&quot;meta总结,html meta,meta属性,meta跳转&quot;&gt;</span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><br />\r\n<span style="color:#B22222;">description：</span>用来告诉搜索引擎你的网站主要内容。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta name=&quot;description&quot;content=&quot;haorooms博客,html的meta总结，meta是html语言head区的一个辅助性标签。&quot;&gt;</span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">viewport：</span>为移动设备添加视口参数</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta name=&quot;viewport&quot; content=&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0&quot; /&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 160px;">content参数说明：&nbsp;<br />\r\nwidth viewport 宽度(数值/device-width)&nbsp;<br />\r\nheight viewport 高度(数值/device-height)&nbsp;<br />\r\ninitial-scale 初始缩放比例&nbsp;<br />\r\nmaximum-scale 最大缩放比例&nbsp;<br />\r\nminimum-scale 最小缩放比例&nbsp;<br />\r\nuser-scalable 是否允许用户缩放(yes/no)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><br />\r\n<span style="color:#B22222;">robots：</span>用来告诉搜索机器人哪些页面需要索引，哪些页面不需要索引。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta name=&quot;robots&quot;content=&quot;none&quot;&gt;</span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 160px;">content的参数有all,none,index,noindex,follow,nofollow。默认是all。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 160px;">具体参数如下：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 160px;">信息参数为all：文件将被检索，且页面上的链接可以被查询；</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 160px;">信息参数为none：文件将不被检索，且页面上的链接不可以被查询；</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 160px;">信息参数为index：文件将被检索；</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 160px;">信息参数为follow：页面上的链接可以被查询；</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 160px;">信息参数为noindex：文件将不被检索，但页面上的链接可以被查询；</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 160px;">信息参数为nofollow：文件将被检索，但页面上的链接不可以被查询；</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">author：</span>标注网页的作者</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta name=&quot;author&quot;content=&quot;root,root@xxxx.com&quot;&gt;</span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">revised：</span>定义页面的最新版本</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta name=&quot;revised&quot; content=&quot;Frank, 2016/3/1&quot; /&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><br />\r\n<span style="color:#B22222;">generator：</span>代表说明网站的采用的什么软件制作（编辑器）。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta name=&quot;generator&quot;content=&quot;信息参数&quot;/&gt;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">COPYRIGHT：</span>代表说明网站版权信息</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;META NAME=&quot;COPYRIGHT&quot;CONTENT=&quot;信息参数&quot;&gt;</span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><br />\r\n<span style="color:#B22222;">revisit-after：</span>代表网站重访,7days代表7天，依此类推。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;META name=&quot;revisit-after&quot;CONTENT=&quot;7days&quot;&gt;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">禁止数字识自动别为电话号码：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta name=&quot;format-detection&quot; content=&quot;telephone=no&quot; /&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">不让android识别邮箱：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta name=&quot;format-detection&quot; content=&quot;email=no&quot; /&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">添加到主屏后的标题（iOS6开始）：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta name=&quot;apple-mobile-web-app-title&quot; content=&quot;标题&quot; /&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">设置状态栏的背景颜色（ISO 设备）：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta name=&quot;apple-mobile-web-app-title&quot; content=&quot;yes&quot; /&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">是否启用 WebApp 全屏模式（ISO 设备）：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta name=&quot;apple-mobile-web-app-capable&quot; content=&quot;yes&quot; /&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">设置状态栏的背景颜色（ISO 设备）：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta name=&quot;apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style&quot; content=&quot;black-translucent&quot; /&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 160px;">注：只有在 &quot;apple-mobile-web-app-capable&quot; content=&quot;yes&quot; 时生效<br />\r\ncontent 参数：<br />\r\ndefault 默认值，网页内容从状态栏底部开始&nbsp;<br />\r\nblack 状态栏背景是黑色，网页内容从状态栏底部开始&nbsp;<br />\r\nblack-translucent 状态栏背景是黑色半透明，网页内容充满整个屏幕，顶部会被状态栏遮挡</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">添加智能 App 广告条 Smart App Banner，告诉浏览器这个网站对应的app，并在页面上显示下载banner（ISO 设备）：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta name=&quot;apple-itunes-app&quot; content=&quot;app-id=myAppStoreID, affiliate-data=myAffiliateData, app-argument=myURL&quot;&gt;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">磁贴颜色（Windows 8）：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta name=&quot;msapplication-TileColor&quot; content=&quot;#000&quot; /&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">磁贴图标（Windows 8）：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta name=&quot;msapplication-TileImage&quot; content=&quot;icon.png&quot; /&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong><span style="color:#B22222;">http-equiv属性：</span></strong>相当于http的文件头作用，它可以向浏览器传回一些有用的信息，以帮助正确和精确地显示网页内容。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><strong>语法格式：</strong>&lt;meta http-equiv=&quot;参数&quot;content=&quot;参数变量值&quot;&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><strong>常用参数</strong>如下：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">X-UA-Compatible</span>：声明文档的兼容模式</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta http-equiv=&quot;X-UA-Compatible&quot; content=&quot;IE=Edge,chrome=1&quot;/&gt;</span></span> //指示IE以目前可用的最高模式显示内容</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">Expires</span>(期限)：可以用于设定网页的到期时间。一旦网页过期，必须到服务器上重新传输。(注意：必须使用GMT的时间格式)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta http-equiv=&quot;expires&quot;content=&quot;Fri,12Jan200118:18:18GMT&quot;&gt;</span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">Pragma</span>(cache模式)：禁止浏览器从本地计算机的缓存中访问页面内容。(注意：这样设定，访问者将无法脱机浏览)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta http-equiv=&quot;Pragma&quot;content=&quot;no-cache&quot;&gt;</span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">Refresh</span>(刷新)：自动刷新并指向新页面。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta http-equiv=&quot;Refresh&quot;content=&quot;2;URL=http://www.haorooms.com&quot;&gt;</span></span> //(注意其中的2是指停留2秒钟后自动刷新到URL网址；后面的引号，分别在秒数的前面和网址的后面)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt; Meta HTTP-EQUIV=&quot;refresh&quot; content=&quot;6; url=http://fym888.nease.net&quot; &gt;</span></span> //让一个页面过上一定的时间，自动转到另一个页面或者站点去<br />\r\n<span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt; Meta HTTP-EQUIV=&quot;refresh&quot; content=&quot;6; url=page1.htm&quot; &gt;</span></span> //若是与你当前网页在同一目录下，可以直接写上文件名</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">Set-Cookie</span>(cookie设定)：如果网页过期，那么存盘的cookie将被删除。(注意：必须使用GMT的时间格式)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta http-equiv=&quot;Set-Cookie&quot;content=&quot;cookie value=xxx;expires=Friday,12-Jan-200118:18:18GMT；path=/&quot;&gt;</span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">Window-target</span>(显示窗口的设定)：强制页面在当前窗口以独立页面显示。(注意：用来防止别人在框架里调用自己的页面)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta http-equiv=&quot;Window-target&quot;content=&quot;_top&quot;&gt;</span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">content-Type</span>(显示字符集的设定)：设定页面使用的字符集。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta http-equiv=&quot;content-Type&quot;content=&quot;text/html;charset=gb2312&quot;&gt;</span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 160px;">具体如下：<br />\r\ncharset=GB2312时，代表说明网站是采用的编码是简体中文；<br />\r\ncharset=BIG5时，代表说明网站是采用的编码是繁体中文；<br />\r\ncharset=iso-2022-jp时，代表说明网站是采用的编码是日文；<br />\r\ncharset=ks_c_5601时，代表说明网站是采用的编码是韩文；<br />\r\ncharset=ISO-8859-1时，代表说明网站是采用的编码是英文；<br />\r\ncharset=UTF-8时，代表世界通用的语言编码；</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;">等同与html5如下写法：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 160px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta charset=&quot;</span></span><span style="color: rgb(128, 0, 128); background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">gb2312</span><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&quot;&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">content-Language</span>（显示语言的设定）</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta http-equiv=&quot;Content-Language&quot;content=&quot;zh-cn&quot;/&gt;</span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">Cache-Control</span>：指定请求和响应遵循的缓存机制。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta http-equiv=&quot;Cache-Control&quot; CONTENT=&quot;no-cache&quot;&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;">- 在请求消息或响应消息中设置Cache-Control并不会修改另一个消息处理过程中的缓存处理过程；</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;">- 请求时的缓存指令包括no-cache、no-store、max-age、max-stale、min-fresh、on<br />\r\nly-if-cached；</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;">- 响应消息中的指令包括public、private、no-cache、no-store、no-transform、must-revalidate、proxy-revalidate、max-age；</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 160px;">各个消息中的指令含义如下：<br />\r\n* Public指示响应可被任何缓存区缓存<br />\r\n* Private指示对于单个用户的整个或部分响应消息，不能被共享缓存处理。这允许服务器仅仅描述当用户的部分响应消息，此响应消息对于其他用户的请求无效<br />\r\n* no-cache指示请求或响应消息不能缓存<br />\r\n* no-store用于防止重要的信息被无意的发布。在请求消息中发送将使得请求和响应消息都不使用缓存。<br />\r\n* max-age指示客户机可以接收生存期不大于指定时间（以秒为单位）的响应<br />\r\n* min-fresh指示客户机可以接收响应时间小于当前时间加上指定时间的响应<br />\r\n* max-stale指示客户机可以接收超出超时期间的响应消息；如果指定max-stale消息的值，那么客户机可以接收超出超时期指定值之内的响应消息。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">imagetoolbar：</span>指定是否显示图片工具栏，当为false代表不显示，当为true代表显示。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta http-equiv=&quot;imagetoolbar&quot;content=&quot;false&quot;/&gt;</span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">Content-Script-Type</span>：W3C网页规范，指明页面中脚本的类型。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;Meta http-equiv=&quot;Content-Script-Type&quot;Content=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;</span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">refresh</span>：刷新<br />\r\n<span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta http-equiv=&quot;refresh&quot; content=&quot;8&quot; /&gt;</span></span> //每 8 秒刷新一次页面</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">Page-Enter、Page-Exit</span> (进入与退出)：这个是页面被载入和调出时的一些特效（只用于IE）</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;Meta http-equiv=&quot;Page-Enter&quot; Content=&quot;blendTrans(Duration=0.5)&quot;&gt;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;Meta http-equiv=&quot;Page-Exit&quot; Content=&quot;blendTrans(Duration=0.5)&quot;&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;">注意：blendTrans是动态滤镜的一种，产生渐隐效果。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;">另一种动态滤镜RevealTrans也可以用于页面进入与退出效果:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 160px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;Meta http-equiv=&quot;Page-Enter&quot; Content=&quot;revealTrans(duration=x, transition=y)&quot;&gt;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;Meta http-equiv=&quot;Page-Exit&quot; Content=&quot;revealTrans(duration=x, transition=y)&quot;&gt;</span></span><br />\r\nDuration 表示滤镜特效的持续时间(单位：秒)<br />\r\nTransition 滤镜类型。表示使用哪种特效，取值为0-23。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 160px;">（详情查看：<a href="http://www.haorooms.com/post/liulanq_think_ie" target="_blank"><span style="color:#B22222;"><span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">http://www.haorooms.com/post/liulanq_think_ie</span></span></a>）</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">Pics-label</span> (网页RSAC等级评定)：在IE的Internet选项中有一项内容设置，可以防止浏览一些受限制的网站，而网站的限制级别就是通过该参数来设置的。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;META http-equiv=&quot;Pics-label&quot; Contect=&quot;(PICS－1.1&#39;http://www.rsac.org/ratingsv01.html&#39; I gen comment &#39;RSACi North America Sever&#39; by &#39;inet@microsoft.com&#39; for &#39;http://www.microsoft.com&#39; on &#39;1997.06.30T14:21－0500&#39; r(n0 s0 v0 l0))&quot;&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 160px;">HTML里面meta &lt;wbr&gt;name标签的属性注意：不要将级别设置的太高。RSAC的评估系统提供了一种用来评价Web站点内容的标准。用户可以设置 Microsoft Internet Explorer（IE3.0以上）来排除包含有色情和暴力内容的站点。上面这个例子中的HTML取自 Microsoft的主页。代码中的（n 0 s 0 v 0 l 0）表示该站点不包含不健康内容。级别的评定是由RSAC，即美国娱乐委员会的评级机构评定的，如果你想进一步了解RSAC评估系统的等级内容，或者你需要评价自己的网站，可以访问RSAC的站点：http://www.rsac.org/。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 160px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">MSThemeCompatible</span> (XP主题)：是否在IE中关闭 xp 的主题</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;Meta http-equiv=&quot;MSThemeCompatible&quot; Content=&quot;Yes&quot;&gt;</span></span><br />\r\n注意：关闭 xp 的蓝色立体按钮系统显示样式，从而和win2k 很象。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">IE6</span> (页面生成器)：页面生成器generator，是ie6</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;Meta http-equiv=&quot;IE6&quot; Content=&quot;Generator&quot;&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">Content-Script-Type</span> (脚本相关)：这是近来W3C的规范，指明页面中脚本的类型。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;Meta http-equiv=&quot;Content-Script-Type&quot; Content=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>scheme属性：设置或返回用于解释 content 属性的值的格式。（scheme 属性用于指定要用来翻译属性值的方案。其值可以是一个格式，也可以是一个URI；此方案应该在由 &lt;head&gt; 标签的 profile 属性指定的概况文件中进行了定义？）</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="color:#800080;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&lt;meta name=&quot;revised&quot; content=&quot;2006-11-03&quot; scheme=&quot;YYYY-MM-DD&quot; /&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>疑问;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;&lt;meta http-equiv=&quot;charset&quot; content=&quot;iso-8859-1&quot;&gt;</p>\r\n', '2016-11-22 03:11:32', '2018-12-26 17:22:11', 48, 0, ''),
(112, '', 0, 'html兼容', NULL, '', '<p>针对ie版本的兼容html代码：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">1. &lt;!--[if !IE]&gt;&lt;!--&gt; 除IE外都可识别 &lt;!--&lt;![endif]--&gt;<br />\r\n2. &lt;!--[if IE]&gt; 所有的IE可识别 &lt;![endif]--&gt;<br />\r\n3. &lt;!--[if IE 5.0]&gt; 只有IE5.0可以识别 &lt;![endif]--&gt;<br />\r\n4. &lt;!--[if IE 5]&gt; 仅IE5.0与IE5.5可以识别 &lt;![endif]--&gt;<br />\r\n5. &lt;!--[if gt IE 5.0]&gt; IE5.0以及IE5.0以上版本都可以识别 &lt;![endif]--&gt;<br />\r\n6. &lt;!--[if IE 6]&gt; 仅IE6可识别 &lt;![endif]--&gt;<br />\r\n7. &lt;!--[if lt IE 6]&gt; IE6以及IE6以下版本可识别 &lt;![endif]--&gt;<br />\r\n8.&lt;!--[if lte IE 6]&gt;小于或等于IE6浏览&lt;![endif]--&gt;<br />\r\n9. &lt;!--[if gte IE 6]&gt; IE6以及IE6以上版本可识别 &lt;![endif]--&gt;<br />\r\n10. &lt;!--[if IE 7]&gt; 仅IE7可识别 &lt;![endif]--&gt;<br />\r\n11. &lt;!--[if lt IE 7]&gt; IE7以及IE7以下版本可识别 &lt;![endif]--&gt;<br />\r\n12. &lt;!--[if gte IE 7]&gt; IE7以及IE7以上版本可识别 &lt;![endif]--&gt;<br />\r\n-----------------------------------------<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;lte：就是Less than or equal to的简写，也就是小于或等于的意思。<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;lt ：就是Less than的简写，也就是小于的意思。<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;gte：就是Greater than or equal to的简写，也就是大于或等于的意思。<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;gt ：就是Greater than的简写，也就是大于的意思。<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;! ：就是不等于的意思，跟javascript里的不等于判断符相同</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>让IE9之前的版本支持Html5的兼容方法：<br />\r\n&lt;!--[if lt IE 9]&gt;<br />\r\n&lt;script src=&quot;http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;<br />\r\n&lt;![endif]--&gt;</p>\r\n', '2016-11-22 03:21:21', '2018-12-26 18:08:56', 52, 0, ''),
(113, '', 0, '基础', NULL, '', '<p>&lt;form name=&quot;form&quot; action=&quot;abc.php&quot; method=&quot;post&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot; enctype=&quot;multipart/form-data&quot;&gt;&nbsp;<br />\r\n...<br />\r\n&lt;/form&gt;<br />\r\n--&nbsp;form必要属性method=&quot;get&quot;or&quot;post&quot;or&quot;request&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-- 如需要图片上传，必须要加enctype=&quot;multipart/form-data&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>表单控件：(&nbsp;<a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/html5/att_input_type.asp" target="_blank">http://www.w3school.com.cn/html5/att_input_type.asp</a>&nbsp;)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">-- input<br />\r\n-- select<br />\r\n-- textarea<br />\r\n-- button<br />\r\n-- output<br />\r\n-- keygen</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="static/html_form.html" target="_blank"><span style="color:#B22222;"><span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">form默认显示效果</span></span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2016-11-22 03:31:15', '2018-12-26 17:39:43', 50, 0, ''),
(114, '', 0, 'iframe', NULL, '', '<p>iframe：创建包含另外一个文档的内联框架（即行内框架）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>---------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&lt;iframe src=&quot;URL&quot; width=&quot;200&quot; height=&quot;200&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">frameborder：规定是否显示框架周围的边框。<br />\r\nheight：规定 iframe 的高度。<br />\r\nlongdesc：规定一个页面，该页面包含了有关 iframe 的较长描述。<br />\r\nmarginheight：定义 iframe 的顶部和底部的边距。<br />\r\nmarginwidth：定义 iframe 的左侧和右侧的边距。<br />\r\nname：规定 iframe 的名称。<br />\r\nsandbox：用一系列对 &lt;iframe&gt; 中内容的额外限制。<br />\r\nscrolling：规定是否在 iframe 中显示滚动条。<br />\r\nseamless：规定 &lt;iframe&gt; 看上去像是包含文档的一部分。<br />\r\nsrc：规定在 iframe 中显示的文档的 URL。<br />\r\nsrcdoc：规定在 &lt;iframe&gt; 中显示的页面的 HTML 内容。<br />\r\nwidth：定义 iframe 的宽度。</p>\r\n', '2018-12-25 08:41:17', '2018-12-26 17:52:12', 71, 0, ''),
(115, '', 0, '实例', NULL, '', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 如leftFrame的链接要在rightFrame显示---给rightFrame加上id=right,再给leftFrame加上target=right<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;父窗口js获取子窗口的html元素：<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$(window.frames[&quot;view_list&quot;].document).find(&quot;.className&quot;)<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;父窗口js刷新子窗口：<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;window.frames[&quot;view_list&quot;].document.location.reload();</p>\r\n', '2018-12-25 08:32:32', '2018-12-26 20:03:37', 71, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `point` (`id`, `pid`, `sort`, `title`, `attr`, `description`, `extend`, `createdAt`, `updatedAt`, `lineId`, `recom`, `subFieldSetting`) VALUES
(116, '', 0, 'input 控件', NULL, '', '<p>hidden --<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;input type=&quot;hidden&quot; &nbsp;id=&quot;hiddenField&quot; &nbsp;name=&quot;hiddenField&quot; &nbsp;placeholder=&quot;hiddenvalue&quot; value=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;<br />\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\ntext --<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; id=&quot;username&quot; name=&quot;username&quot; value=&quot;uservalue&quot; size=&quot;10&quot; maxlength=&quot;25&quot; /&gt;<br />\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\npassword --<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;input type=&quot;password&quot; id=&quot;pass&quot; name=&quot;pass&quot; value=&quot;12345&quot; size=&quot;15&quot; maxlength=&quot;25&quot; /&gt;<br />\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\nradio --&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;label for=&quot;male&quot;&gt;男&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; value=&quot;1&quot; id=&quot;male&quot; name=&quot;sex&quot; checked=&quot;checked&quot; /&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;label for=&quot;female&quot;&gt;女&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; value=&quot;2&quot; id=&quot;female&quot; name=&quot;sex&quot; /&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;label for=&quot;secret&quot;&gt;保密&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; value=&quot;3&quot; id=&quot;secret&quot; name=&quot;sex&quot; disabled=&quot;disabled&quot; /&gt;<br />\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\ncheckbox --<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;label for=&quot;fav1&quot;&gt;计算机&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; value=&quot;1&quot; id=&quot;fav1&quot; name=&quot;fav&quot; checked=&quot;checked&quot; /&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;label for=&quot;fav2&quot;&gt;旅游&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; value=&quot;2&quot; id=&quot;fav2&quot; name=&quot;fav&quot; disabled=&quot;disabled&quot; /&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;label for=&quot;fav3&quot;&gt;购物&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; value=&quot;3&quot; id=&quot;fav3&quot; name=&quot;fav&quot; /&gt;<br />\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\nfile --<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;input type=&quot;file&quot; id=&quot;myimage&quot; name=&quot;myimage&quot; size=&quot;35&quot; maxlength=&quot;255&quot; /&gt;<br />\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\nsubmit --<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;input type=&quot;submit&quot; value=&quot;submit&quot; id=&quot;submit&quot; name=&quot;submit&quot; /&gt;<br />\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\nbutton --<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;input type=&quot;button&quot; value=&quot;submit&quot; id=&quot;button&quot; name=&quot;button&quot; /&gt;<br />\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\nreset --<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;input type=&quot;reset&quot; value=&quot;reset&quot; id=&quot;reset&quot; name=&quot;submit&quot; /&gt;<br />\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\nimage --<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;input type=&quot;image&quot; src=&quot;aaa.png&quot; alt=&quot;aaa&quot; /&gt;<br />\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\nsearch --<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;input type=&quot;search&quot; class=&quot;keyword&quot; name=&quot;keyword&quot; placeholder=&quot;...&quot; /&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ------placeholder：描述文本区域预期值的简短提示，不输入值是focus()和blur()提示不影响；&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;------label for=&quot;控件的id&quot; //点击label对应id的控件就获取焦点<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;------size:规定输入[显示]字段的宽度（输入框宽度）<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;------maxlength:规定输入字段中的字符的最大长度<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ------autocomplete:默认&#39;on&#39;,浏览器将根据之前访问本页时保存的值预填表单控件；&#39;off&#39;关闭记录</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Checkbox &amp; radio:<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;------checked=&quot;checked&quot;默认选定<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;------disabled=&quot;disabled&quot;不能选<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;------name必须有且一样<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;------id要不同<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;------value排序区分不同值</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;text:<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;------readonly=&quot;readonly&quot;只读</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; image:<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ------创建一个图像控件，该控件单击后将导致表单立即被提交。本身就是个提交按钮，和submit功能一样</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; search:<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ------用于手机端，手机输入键盘会有一个&quot;搜索&quot;按钮</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>.disabled手机显示文字不清楚</p>\r\n\r\n<p>input[disabled],input:disabled,input.disabled{&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>color:&nbsp;#999;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-webkit-text-fill-color:#999;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-webkit-opacity:1;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>opacity:&nbsp;1;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(234, 248, 230);">input不能有伪类： 如:after</span></p>\r\n', '2016-11-22 03:31:49', '2018-12-26 20:01:26', 50, 0, ''),
(117, '', 0, 'button 控件', NULL, '', '<p>&lt;button type=&quot;submit&quot; form=&quot;nameform&quot; value=&quot;submit&quot;&gt;提交&lt;/button&gt;<br />\r\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ------form 属性规定按钮属于一个或多个表单;值必须是按钮所属表单的 id;如需引用一个以上的表单，请使用空格分隔的列表。</p>\r\n', '2016-11-22 03:32:17', '2018-12-26 17:42:40', 50, 0, ''),
(118, '', 0, 'select 控件', NULL, '', '<p>&lt;select size=&quot;1&quot; id=&quot;select&quot; name=&quot;select&quot;&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;option value=&quot;1&quot;&gt;很全面,很好&lt;/option&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;option value=&quot;2&quot;&gt;一般般吧,还要努力&lt;/option&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;option value=&quot;3&quot;&gt;有很多问题,不过还可以&lt;/option&gt;<br />\r\n&lt;/select&gt;<br />\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\n&lt;select size=&quot;10&quot; multiple=&quot;multiple&quot; id=&quot;multipleselect&quot; name=&quot;multipleselect&quot;&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;option value=&quot;xhtml&quot;&gt;XHTML&lt;/option&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;option value=&quot;css&quot; selected=&quot;selected&quot;&gt;CSS&lt;/option&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;option value=&quot;javascript&quot;&gt;JAVASCRIPT&lt;/option&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;optgroup label=&quot;OPTGROUP&quot;&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;option value=&quot;xml&quot;&gt;XML&lt;/option&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;option value=&quot;php&quot;&gt;PHP&lt;/option&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;option value=&quot;c#&quot;&gt;C#&lt;/option&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;option value=&quot;java&quot;&gt;JAVA&lt;/option&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/optgroup&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;option value=&quot;c++&quot;&gt;C++&lt;/option&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;option value=&quot;perl&quot;&gt;PERL&lt;/option&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;option value=&quot;jquery&quot;&gt;JQUERY&lt;/option&gt;<br />\r\n&lt;/select&gt;<br />\r\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;select：<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;------disabled=&quot;disabled&quot;禁用该下拉列表<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;------size:选中后显示项目数，超出显示滚动条<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;------multiple:按Shift可选择多个选项</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;option：<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;------selected=&quot;selected&quot;默认选中</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;html5新增：<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;------autofocus=&quot;autofocus&quot; //规定在页面加载后文本区域自动获得焦点<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;------form=&quot;#form_id&quot; //规定文本区域所属的一个或多个表单<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;------required=&quot;required&quot; //规定文本区域是必填的</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>自定义select：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">1. absolute覆盖在上面然后opacity:0 (visible:hidden??)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">-<span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">不支持opacity浏览器加上兼容前缀就好</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">-但下拉的option样式不好设置</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">2. js不能控制select下拉，所以要更好得设置下拉的option只能全部自定义了</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">-用标签搭建select的html结构，用js模仿select的下拉及选择功能</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">-最后可把selected的option赋给一个input:hidden随form提交</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2016-11-22 03:32:44', '2018-12-26 17:44:44', 50, 0, ''),
(119, '', 0, 'textarea 控件', NULL, '', '<p>&lt;textarea cols=&quot;50&quot; rows=&quot;10&quot; id=&quot;a&quot; name=&quot;a&quot;&gt;12345&lt;/t^extarea&gt;<br />\r\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;------cols:文本区内的可见宽度（最好用css的width设置）<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;------rows:文本区内的可见行数（最好用css的height设置）<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;------disabled=&quot;disabled&quot; 禁用该文本区</p>\r\n', '2016-11-22 03:33:13', '2018-12-26 20:09:30', 50, 0, ''),
(120, '', 0, '基础属性', NULL, '', '<p><span style="color:#FF0000;">背景：</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>---------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; {<br />\r\n&nbsp; background-color<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :#FFF;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; background-repeat<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :repeat;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :no-repeat;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :repeat-x;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :repeat-y;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; background-position<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :35% 80%;(横坐标 纵坐标)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :right center;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; background-image<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :url(...);<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :none;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; background-attachment (背景图像是否固定或者随着页面的其余部分滚动)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :fixed;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :scroll;<br />\r\n&nbsp; }</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; background:transparent (透明)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><br />\r\n<span style="color:#FF0000;">文本：</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>---------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; {<br />\r\n&nbsp; text-indent<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :1px;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; color<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :#FFFFFF;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; line-height<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :normal;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :1px;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; text-align<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :left;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :right;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :center;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :justify;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; direction (文本的方向 / 书写方向)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :ltr;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :rtl;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; text-decoration<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :overline;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :line-through;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :underline;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :blink;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :none;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; letter-spacing (字符间距)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :normal;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :1px;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; word-spacing (单词间距)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :normal;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :1px;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; white-space (如何处理元素中的空白)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :pre;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :nowrap; (忽略空格和换行，强行在一行内显示所有内容)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :normal;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; text-transform (控制文本的大小写)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :lowercase;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :uppercase;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :capitalize;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :none;<br />\r\n&nbsp; }<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; text-overflow:ellipsis; (超出省略号)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; {overflow:hidden; text-overflow:ellipsis; white-space:nowrap;}//内容超过容器不换行且以省略号结尾</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><br />\r\n<span style="color:#FF0000;">文字：</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>---------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; {<br />\r\n&nbsp; font-family<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :&quot;宋体&quot;;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; font-style<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :italic;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :oblique;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :normal;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; font-size<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :small;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :smaller;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :large;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :larger;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :medium;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :x-small;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :xx-small;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :x-large;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :xx-large;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :1px;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; font-weight<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :bold;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :bolder;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :lighter;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :normal;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :100;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; font-variant (是否以小型大写字母的字体显示文本)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :small-caps;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :normal;<br />\r\n&nbsp; }<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; font-stretch (收缩或拉伸当前的字体系列)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; : &nbsp;normal | narrower | wider&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><br />\r\n<span style="color:#FF0000;">列表：</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>---------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; {<br />\r\n&nbsp; list-style-type<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :circle;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :disc;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :square;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :lower-alpha;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :upper-alpha;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :lower-roman;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :upper-roman;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :decimal;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :none;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; list-style-image<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :url();<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :none;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; list-style-position<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :inside;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :outside;<br />\r\n&nbsp; }</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><br />\r\n<span style="color:#FF0000;">表格：</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>---------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; {<br />\r\n&nbsp; caption-side<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :top;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :bottom;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :left;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :right;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; border-collapse (表格的边框是否被合并为一个单一的边框，还是象在标准的 HTML 中那样分开显示)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :collapse;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :separate;(默认)<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; border-spacing (=cellspacing 也可用td的margin来指定表格的cellspacing)--(用td的padding来指定表格的cellpadding)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :1px;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; empty-cells (是否显示表格中的空单元格（仅用于&ldquo;分离边框&rdquo;模式）)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :hide;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :show;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; table-layout<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :auto; (默认,列宽度由单元格内容设定--单元格随内容拓宽)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :fixed; (列宽由表格宽度和列宽度设定--单元格宽度固定，内容会超出)<br />\r\n&nbsp; }</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><br />\r\n<span style="color:#FF0000;">边框：</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>---------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; {<br />\r\n&nbsp; outline-style<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :dotted;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :dashed;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :solid;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :double;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :groove;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :ridge;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :inset;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :outset;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :hidden;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :none;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; outline-color<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :#FFFFFF;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; outline-width<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :thin;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :thick;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; :medium;<br />\r\n&nbsp; }</p>\r\n', '2016-11-22 05:39:13', '2018-12-26 18:11:51', 54, 0, ''),
(121, '', 0, '文本超出省略号', NULL, '', '<p>单行：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-----------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>.e-{ display:block; white-space:nowrap; overflow:hidden;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;text-overflow:ellipsis;&nbsp;<br />\r\n-o-text-overflow:ellipsis;<br />\r\n}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>多行：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-----------<br />\r\n.e--{<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; display:-webkit-box!important;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; overflow:hidden;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; word-break:break-all;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; -webkit-box-orient:vertical;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; -webkit-line-clamp:2;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;text-overflow:ellipsis;&nbsp;<br />\r\n-o-text-overflow:ellipsis;<br />\r\n}</p>\r\n', '2018-12-25 09:58:14', '2018-12-26 18:15:10', 55, 0, ''),
