(332, '', 0, '重置样式相关', NULL, '', '<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">--重置代码reset.css用了word-wrap:break-word;ie浏览器设置white-space:nowrap无效</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">--white-space,word-wrap,word-break区别</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">--word-wrap:break-word; -&gt;英文单词长度大于整一行</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">--word-break</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">--text-align:justify;<font color="#222222" face="Consolas, Lucida Console, monospace"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;-&gt;两边对齐</span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<hr style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;" />\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">重置代码中body要不要relative？</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;"><a href="http://bbs.blueidea.com/thread-2918577-1-1.html" target="_blank">http://bbs.blueidea.com/thread-2918577-1-1.html</a></p>\r\n', '2017-12-17 12:50:05', '2018-12-26 18:40:47', 73, 0, ''),
(333, '', 0, 'token', NULL, '', '<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px;">html获取最新token：（app - webview）</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px;">JS混合APP前端获取最新Token方法格式定义：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px;">获取最新token方法名：getRefreshToken</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px;">Android 例如：window.WebView.getRefreshToken()<br />\r\nIOS 例如：window.webkit.messageHandlers.intoExpertDetail.postMessage({body: &#39;&#39;});</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px;">方法返回参数：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px;">类型---String</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px;">格式---<br />\r\n获取成功：{&quot;result&quot;:1;&quot;token&quot;:&quot;123456789abcd&quot;}</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px;">获取失败：{&quot;result&quot;:-1;&quot;token&quot;:&quot;&quot;}</p>\r\n', '2017-12-17 12:58:06', '2018-12-27 08:45:23', 59, 0, ''),
(334, '', 0, 'Nginx', NULL, '', '<p>nginx-1.13.1conf的nginx.conf文件 http{}对象内最后加include D:/wwwroot/qmyg_vue/vhosts/*.conf;指向项目的虚拟服务器配置</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">nginx：本目录执行start nginx &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">npm run nginx??</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>-nginx启动打开命令行工具：按住Shift+右击点选&#39;在此处打开命令窗口&#39;</p>\r\n', '2017-12-17 11:33:53', '2017-12-16 23:39:45', 25, 0, ''),
(335, '', 0, '对比', NULL, '', '<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">-Sass的功能比Less强大,基本可以说是一种真正的编程语言了，Less则相对清晰明了,易于上手,对编译环境要求比较宽松</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">-Sass的安装需要Ruby环境，是在服务端处理的，而Less是需要引入less.js来处理Less代码输出css到浏览器，也可以在开发环节使用Less，然后编译成css文件，直接放到项目中，也有 Less.app、SimpleLess、CodeKit.app这样的工具，也有在线编译地址</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">-Sass的缩排语法，对于写惯css前端的web开发者来说很不直观，也不能将css代码加入到Sass里面，因此sass语法进行了改良，Sass 3就变成了Scss(sassy css)。与原来的语法兼容，只是用{}取代了原来的缩进。</p>\r\n', '2017-12-17 12:22:22', '2019-01-03 05:17:23', 86, 0, ''),
(336, '', 0, '杂', NULL, '', '<p>环境变量：如果执行某个命令，系统无法在当前文件夹里找到对应的.exe，那么系统就会去环境变量path包含的路径中挨个找看是否能知道对应的.exe，一旦找到第一个对应的.exe就运行命令，其他的路径下就不找了。如果找不到你就会看到&ldquo;系统找不到某某命令&rdquo;的提示。</p>\r\n', '2017-12-17 12:24:10', '2017-12-17 00:23:41', 95, 0, ''),
(337, '', 0, 'JQ操作DOM', NULL, '', '<p style="line-height:16px;">文档：<a href="http://jquery.cuishifeng.cn/" target="_blank">http://jquery.cuishifeng.cn/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">选择器参考：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">-----------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-$(&quot;div,span,p.myClass&quot;)<br />\r\n-$(&quot;label + input&quot;) //匹配所有label的next元素input</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-$(&quot;form ~ input&quot;) //匹配form的所有siblings元素input</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-$(&quot;input:not(:checked)&quot;)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-$(&quot;td:parent&quot;) //匹配含有子元素或者文本的元素td</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-$(&quot;tr:hidden&quot;) &amp; $(&quot;tr:visible&quot;)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-$(&quot;input[id][name$=&#39;man&#39;]&quot;) //复合属性选择器,同时又id属性和name属性等于&#39;man&#39;的input</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-$(&#39;li:first&#39;); //获取第一个元素</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-$(&quot;ul li:first-child&quot;) //匹配第一个子元素</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-$(&quot;ul li:nth-child(2)&quot;) //在每个 ul 查找第 2 个li (从1开始)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-$(&quot;ul li:eq(2)&quot;) //第一个ul找第2个li?(从0开始)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-$(&quot;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hello&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&quot;)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-$(&quot;img&quot;).get(0);</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-$(&#39;li&#39;).index(document.getElementById(&#39;bar&#39;)); //1，传递一个DOM对象，返回这个对象在原先集合中的索引位置</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-$(&#39;li&#39;).index($(&#39;#bar&#39;)); //1，传递一个jQuery对象</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-$(&#39;li&#39;).index($(&#39;li:gt(0)&#39;)); //1，传递一组jQuery对象，返回这个对象中第一个元素在原先集合中的索引位置</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-$(&#39;#bar&#39;).index(&#39;li&#39;); //1，传递一个选择器，返回#bar在所有li中的索引位置</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-$(&#39;#bar&#39;).index(); //1，不传递参数，返回这个元素在同辈中的索引位置。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-$.grep( [0,1,2], function(n,i){ return n &gt; 0;});//过滤数组中小于 0 的元素</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-$(&quot;p&quot;).contents().not(&quot;[nodeType=1]&quot;).wrap(&quot;&lt;b/&gt;&quot;);</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-$(&quot;iframe&quot;).contents().find(&quot;body&quot;) .append(&quot;I&#39;m in an iframe!&quot;);</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">方法参考：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">-----------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-detach():从DOM中删除所有匹配的元素。这个方法不会把匹配的元素从jQuery对象中删除，因而可以在将来再使用这些匹配的元素。与remove()不同的是，所有绑定的事件、附加的数据等都会保留下来。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>获取元素名：prop(&quot;tagName&quot;)</p>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>获取屏幕高度用$(window).height();【页面必需包含&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML&gt;&lt;html&gt;...&lt;/html&gt;】</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', '2017-12-17 12:28:22', '2018-12-27 06:22:19', 57, 0, ''),
(338, '', 0, 'cookie', NULL, '', '<p>问题：<br />\r\n- Domain以及path属性？<br />\r\n- 清空要对应cookie的Domain以及path怎么写？</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">// 设置cookie</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">function setCookie(cname,cvalue,exdays){</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">&nbsp; &nbsp; var d = new Date();</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">&nbsp; &nbsp; d.setTime(d.getTime()+(exdays*24*60*60*1000));</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">&nbsp; &nbsp; var expires = &quot;expires=&quot;+d.toGMTString();</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">&nbsp; &nbsp; document.cookie = cname+&quot;=&quot;+cvalue+&quot;; &quot;+expires;</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">}</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">// 获取cookie</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">function getCookie(cname){</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">&nbsp; &nbsp; var name = cname + &quot;=&quot;;</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">&nbsp; &nbsp; var ca = document.cookie.split(&#39;;&#39;);</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">&nbsp; &nbsp; for(var i=0; i&lt;ca.length; i++) {</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; var c = ca[i].trim();</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; if (c.indexOf(name)==0) { return c.substring(name.length,c.length); }</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">&nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">&nbsp; &nbsp; return &quot;&quot;;</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">}</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">// 清空cookie</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">function clearCookie(){&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;var keys=document.cookie.match(/[^ =;]+(?==)/g);&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;if (keys) {&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;for (var i = keys.length; i--;) {</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;document.cookie=keys[i]+&#39;=0;expires=&#39; + new Date( 0).toUTCString()&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;}</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 235, 215);">}&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<p>设置：<br />\r\ndocument.cookie = &quot;key=value; expires=xxx&quot;;&nbsp;<br />\r\n// expires为过期时间，值如Thu, 18 Dec 2043 12:00:00 GMT<br />\r\n// 设置expires可参考上面方法setCookie</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>读取：<br />\r\nvar x = document.cookie; // 返回字符串的值类似于：a1=111;a2=222<br />\r\n// 获取某个参数的值需要对上面返回值做字符串处理，如上方法getCookie(key)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>修改：<br />\r\ndocument.cookie = &quot;key=value2; expires=xxx&quot;;&nbsp;<br />\r\n// 跟创建一样，它会把value2覆盖之前key的值</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>删除：<br />\r\ndocument.cookie = &quot;key=; expires=yyy&quot;; // 把expires设置成过去的时间就好<br />\r\n// 删除时不必指定 cookie 的值</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\n- cookie存储数据比较少，只有几k</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">设置：$.cookie(&#39;test&#39;,&#39;123&#39;);</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">获取：$.cookie(&#39;test&#39;);</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">清空：$.cookie(&#39;test&#39;,&#39;&#39;);</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">php获取：$_COOKIE(&#39;test&#39;);</p>\r\n', '2017-12-17 12:36:24', '2018-12-27 08:44:55', 59, 0, '');
