(395, '', 0, '安装', NULL, '', '<p>问题：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- /log文件夹要建吗</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 安装是如何自定义安装路径而不会报错</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 下载安装程序：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- 地址：<a href="https://www.mongodb.com/download-center/community">https://www.mongodb.com/download-center/community</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- 下载文件如：mongodb-win32-x86_64-2008plus-ssl-4.0.4-signed</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- 之前下了一个不用安装直接是安装后的压缩文件，没搞起来</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 安装：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- 中间有一项选custom，一路确定，后面有一个需要把左下角的勾去掉</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- 遇到过的问题：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">- 没有把左下角的勾去掉，后面会一直安装很久很久，后来取消重来</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">- 上面重来后报错，应该是有些关联程序没有清完，任务管理器-性能-资源监控器-CUP-关联句柄填程序名称，把下面列举的关联程序结束掉就好</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">- 修改了安装路径后面会报...Verify that you have sufficient privileges to start system services...，取消重来不改安装路径就很快装完了</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 配置：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- 默认安装到了C:/Program Files/MongoDB</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- 在里面的/data文件夹内新建文件夹/db</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- cmd进到程序bin文件里输入：mongod -dbpath&nbsp;C:/Program Files/MongoDB/Server/4.0/data/db</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">- 右击Git Bash输入命令无效，应该要配置到环境变量才可以吧</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- 浏览器访问http://localhost:27017/显示 It looks like you are trying to...代表成功了</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mac安装：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 先安装brew</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- $ brew install mongodb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- $ brew services start mongodb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- $ mongo //启动</p>\r\n', '2018-11-27 04:02:03', '2019-02-01 04:58:34', 101, 0, ''),
(396, '', 0, '命令', NULL, '', '<p><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">db：数据库</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">collection：集合（类似于sql数据表）</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">document：文档（类似于sql一条记录）？</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">-----------------------------------------------------</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">$&nbsp;mongo&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;#启动mongoDB</span></p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">$&nbsp;show dbs;                            #查看全部数据库\r\n</span></pre>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">$ use &lt;db name&gt;;                  #切换数据库\r\n\r\n$&nbsp;show collections;                  #显示当前数据库中的集合</span>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<span style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;">$ db.foo.find();                       #当前数据库的foo集合进行数据查找（由于没有条件，会列出所有数据） \r\n$ db.foo.find( { a : 1 } );        #条件是：属性a=1</span></pre>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">$ db; 或者 $ db.getName();&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;#查看当前所在数据库 </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">$ db.help();&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;#显示数据库操作命令</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">$ db.foo.help();&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;#显示当前数据库foo集合的操作命令</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><font face="verdana, geneva, sans-serif">参考：</font><a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/JeremyWYL/p/7809318.html" target="_blank">https://www.cnblogs.com/JeremyWYL/p/7809318.html​</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>高级例子：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/QQ736238785/article/details/79871067" target="_blank">https://blog.csdn.net/QQ736238785/article/details/79871067</a></p>\r\n', '2018-11-27 04:30:36', '2018-11-27 04:33:01', 101, 0, ''),
(397, '', 0, '实例', NULL, '', '<p><span style="color:#FF0000;">让表头悬浮</span>：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 一种是复制一个表，高度为表头高度（即只显示表头），悬浮时显示覆盖在表上</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 另一样用translateY：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="color:#0000FF;">$(表).on(&#39;scroll&#39;,function (e) {</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#0000FF;">var scrollTop = this.scrollTop;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="color:#0000FF;">$(表头).style.transform = &#39;translateY(&#39; + scrollTop + &#39;px)&#39;;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="color:#0000FF;">})</span></p>\r\n', '2018-11-27 04:48:06', '2018-12-26 17:26:51', 51, 0, ''),
(398, '', 0, 'BEM', NULL, '', '<p>英文文档：<a href="https://en.bem.info/methodology/quick-start/" target="_blank">https://en.bem.info/methodology/quick-start/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>中文参考：<a href="http://laichuanfeng.com/reproduce/bem-key-concepts/" target="_blank">http://laichuanfeng.com/reproduce/bem-key-concepts/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div>Block - 区块 [ .o-menu ]</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Element - 元素 [ .o-menu__item ]</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Modifier - 修饰符</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;修饰块：[ .o-menu--color ]&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;修饰元素：[ .o-menu__item--selected ]</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:14px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">其他类似：</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:14px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">SUIT CSS：<a href="https://www.zcfy.cc/article/introduction-to-suit-css-web-design-weekly-2217.html?utm_source=tuicool&amp;utm_medium=referral" target="_blank">https://www.zcfy.cc/article/introduction-to-suit-css-web-design-weekly-2217.html?utm_source=tuicool&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n', '2018-12-01 11:29:39', '2019-03-01 04:14:11', 103, 0, ''),
(399, '', 0, 'SMACSS', NULL, '', '<div>英文官网：<a href="https://smacss.com/" target="_blank">https://smacss.com/</a></div>\r\n\r\n<div>参考：<a href="https://www.aliyun.com/jiaocheng/642337.html?spm=5176.100033.2.6.72fc3d6c68J27r" target="_blank">https://www.aliyun.com/jiaocheng/642337.html?spm=5176.100033.2.6.72fc3d6c68J27r</a></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>SMACSS：（Scalable and Modular Architecture for CSS）</div>\r\n\r\n<div>基本理念是可扩展和模块化</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>把 CSS 样式规则分成以下类别：</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">基础：该类别中包含的是默认的 CSS 样式。作为其他样式的基础。</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">布局：该类别中包含与页面布局相关的 CSS 样式，用来进行模块的排列（前缀&ldquo;l-&rdquo;）</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">模块：该类别中包含的是可复用的模块的 CSS 样式。（前缀是模块名称）</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">状态：该类别中的 CSS 样式用来描述布局和模块在不同状态下的外观。比如在不同的屏幕尺寸下，布局会发生变化。标签式模块的每个标签页可以有显示或隐藏的状态（前缀&ldquo;is-&rdquo;）</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">主题：该类别和状态类似，只不过是用来改变布局和模块的视觉效果</div>\r\n', '2018-12-01 13:11:40', '2019-03-01 03:50:47', 103, 0, ''),
(400, '', 0, 'ACSS', NULL, '', '<p>英文官网：<a href="https://acss.io/" target="_blank">https://acss.io/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ACSS：（Atomic CSS）原子化 CSS<br />\r\n- 原则是把 CSS 样式打散成尽可能小的部分，每个 CSS 类只对应一条样式规则，从而达到最大化的可复用性<br />\r\n- 如：.f10{font-size:10px} .m10{margin:10px;}等</p>\r\n', '2018-12-01 13:12:32', '2019-03-01 03:51:12', 103, 0, ''),
(401, '', 0, 'OOCSS', NULL, '', '<div>英文官网：<a href="http://oocss.org/" target="_blank">http://oocss.org/</a></div>\r\n\r\n<div>参考：<a href="https://www.w3cplus.com/css/oocss-concept" target="_blank">https://www.w3cplus.com/css/oocss-concept</a></div>\r\n\r\n<div>概念篇：<a href="https://www.w3cplus.com/css/oocss-concept" target="_blank">https://www.w3cplus.com/css/oocss-concept</a></div>\r\n\r\n<div>核心篇：<a href="https://www.w3cplus.com/css/oocss-core" target="_blank">https://www.w3cplus.com/css/oocss-core</a></div>\r\n\r\n<div>参考：<a href="https://www.w3cplus.com/css/an-introduction-to-object-oriented-css-oocss.html" target="_blank">https://www.w3cplus.com/css/an-introduction-to-object-oriented-css-oocss.html</a></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>OOCSS（面向对象css）</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- 结构与样式分离 （把布局样式和设计样式独立出来）</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- 容器与内容分离 （把内容从容器中分离出来，换过句话说任何对象（容器），应该适应接受任何形式的内容）</div>\r\n\r\n<div>//OOCSS最关键的一点就是：提高他的灵活性和可重用性</div>\r\n', '2018-12-01 13:13:53', '2019-03-01 03:43:32', 103, 0, ''),
(402, '', 0, 'ITCSS', NULL, '', '<div>ITCSS（Inverted Triangle CSS，即倒三角CSS） 没有明确每一层一定要是什么</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>参考一：</div>\r\n\r\n<div>----------------------------------------------------------------</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>&bull; 设置&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;预处理程序变量和方法（并没有真正的CSS output）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 工具&nbsp;&ndash; Mixin和函数（并没有真正的CSS output）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 族&nbsp;&ndash; 或是你自己的批量代码CSS reset。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 元素&nbsp;&ndash; 不包含类的单一HTML元素选择器</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 对象&nbsp;&ndash; 用于页面架构的类，通常伴随OOCSS方法。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 组件&nbsp;&ndash; 用于美化页面元素的美学类。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Trumps&nbsp;&ndash; 特异性最强的部分，用于覆盖所有倒三角中其他组成部分</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>参考二：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>----------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div># Settings - 设置</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">- 用作抽象类，不生成最后的css</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">- 主要包括：</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">- 基本（Base）</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">- 颜色（Color）</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">- 排版（Typography）</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">- 动画（Animation）</div>\r\n\r\n<div># Tools - 工具</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">- 不生成最后的css，通常是预处理函数</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">- 函数（Functions）</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">- 占位符（Placeholders）</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">- 混合宏（Mixins）</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">- 媒体查询（Media Queries）</div>\r\n\r\n<div># Vendors - 供应商</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">- 指第三方样式</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">- 如reset.css、normalize.css，甚至是Foundation和Bootstrap这样的CSS Frameworks等</div>\r\n\r\n<div># Objects - 对象</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">- 命名空间以o-开头</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">- 常用的对象类如：</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">.o-page：最外层的容器，比如在容器中运用max-width: 100vw和overflow:hidden</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">.o-main：主内容区域的外部容器</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">.o-container：组件的外部容器，通常提供固定的宽度</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">.o-content：实际内容区域的任何额外配置</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">.o-grid：网格布局</div>\r\n\r\n<div># Elements - 元素</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">- 命名空间以e-开头</div>\r\n\r\n<div># Components - 组件</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">- 命名空间以c-开头</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">- 是构成网站一部分的一个小特性</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">- 如button、accordions、sliders、modal等</div>\r\n\r\n<div># Patterns - 模式</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">- 命名空间以p-开头</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">- 模式是组件的组合</div>\r\n\r\n<div># Scopes - 作用域</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">- 命名空间以s-开头</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">- 目的是为我们提供最高的权重，以例我们可以为特定的目的覆盖任何样式</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">- 不建议用，提倡给组件添加修饰符来代替用作用域类来覆盖通用样式</div>\r\n\r\n<div># Utils</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>其他：</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="https://ruby-china.org/topics/37440" target="_blank">https://ruby-china.org/topics/37440</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="https://sdk.cn/news/4578?hmsr=toutiao.io&amp;utm_medium=toutiao.io&amp;utm_source=toutiao.io" target="_blank">https://sdk.cn/news/4578?hmsr=toutiao.io&amp;utm_medium=toutiao.io&amp;utm_source=toutiao.io</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n', '2018-12-01 14:28:54', '2019-03-01 03:50:56', 103, 0, ''),
(403, '', 0, '网址', NULL, '', '<p style="line-height:16px;">命名规范：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">----------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">结合SEM和BIO来改进CSS：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><a href="https://www.w3cplus.com/css/combining-the-powers-of-sem-and-bio-for-improving-css.html" target="_blank">https://www.w3cplus.com/css/combining-the-powers-of-sem-and-bio-for-improving-css.html</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">编写模块化CSS：BEM：</span><a href="https://www.w3cplus.com/css/css-architecture-1.html" target="_blank">https://www.w3cplus.com/css/css-architecture-1.html​</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p id="ibm-pagetitle-h1" style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">从 BEM 谈大型项目中 CSS 的组织和管理：</span><a href="https://www.ibm.com/developerworks/cn/web/1512_chengfu_bem/" target="_blank">https://www.ibm.com/developerworks/cn/web/1512_chengfu_bem/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">CSS制作Facebook的媒体对象：</span><a href="https://www.w3cplus.com/css/facebook-status-message-design-with-css" target="_blank">https://www.w3cplus.com/css/facebook-status-message-design-with-css​</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">合理的css架构：<a href="https://www.oschina.net/translate/thoughtful-css-architecture" target="_blank">https://www.oschina.net/translate/thoughtful-css-architecture</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">css架构的理想与现实：<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/2c6469fcec4a" target="_blank">https://www.jianshu.com/p/2c6469fcec4a</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>语法规范：</p>\r\n\r\n<p data-spm-anchor-id="a2c4e.11155472.blogcont.i0.5190561baA9GYi" style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">CSS语法规范：</span><a href="https://yq.aliyun.com/ziliao/568690" target="_blank">https://yq.aliyun.com/ziliao/568690​</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p data-spm-anchor-id="a2c4e.11155472.blogcont.i0.5190561baA9GYi" style="line-height:16px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;其他：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>bem-tools：<a href="https://github.com/bem-archive/bem-tools" target="_blank">https://github.com/bem-archive/bem-tools</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>// 关于BEM的工具，百度不了多少相关信息，国内应该很少人用吧，比较早期的工具</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>BIO = BEM + ITCSS + OOCSS</p>\r\n', '2018-12-01 14:38:29', '2019-03-01 03:51:25', 103, 0, ''),
(404, '', 0, 'SEM', NULL, '', '<p>参考：<a href="https://www.w3cplus.com/css/combining-the-powers-of-sem-and-bio-for-improving-css.html" target="_blank">https://www.w3cplus.com/css/combining-the-powers-of-sem-and-bio-for-improving-css.html</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SEM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- Scalable（可伸缩性，可重用）<br />\r\n- Extensible（可扩展性）<br />\r\n- Maintainable（可维护性）</p>\r\n', '2018-12-01 15:17:54', '2019-03-01 02:30:57', 103, 0, ''),
(405, '', 0, 'bind()', NULL, '', '<div>参考：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/zztt/p/4122352.html" target="_blank">https://www.cnblogs.com/zztt/p/4122352.html</a></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>bind() 方法的主要作用就是将函数绑定至某个对象，</div>\r\n\r\n<div>bind() 方法会创建一个函数，函数体内this对象的值会被绑定到传入bind() 函数的值。</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>例如，在 f() 函数上调用 bind() 方法并传入参数 obj ，即 f.bind(obj) ，这将返回一个新函数, 新函数会把原始的函数 f() 当做 obj 的方法来调用,就像 obj.f() 似的，当然这时 f() 函数中的 this 对象指向的是 obj</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>--------------------------------------------------------</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">var o = {</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">value: &#39;aaa&#39;,</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">f: function () {</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">var self = this;</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">var fff = function () {</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">console.log(self.value);</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">};</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">fff();</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">}</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">};</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">o.f();</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>以上如果不用self = this，可以用下面的bind(this)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">var o = {</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">value: &#39;aaa&#39;,</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">f: function ()&nbsp;{</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">var fff = function () {</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">console.log(this.value);</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">}.bind(this);</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">fff();</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">}</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">}</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">o.f();</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>--------------------------------------------------------</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">function f(y,z){</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">&nbsp; &nbsp; return this.x+y+z;</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">}</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">var m=f.bind({x:1},2);&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">console.log(m(3));&nbsp; // 6</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>bind()方法会把传入它的第一个实参绑定给f函数体内的this，</div>\r\n\r\n<div>从第二个实参起，将依此传递给原始函数，</div>\r\n\r\n<div>因此{x:1}传递给this,2传递给形参ym(3)调用时的3传递给形参z</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>//bind()方法ES5才有</div>\r\n', '2018-12-04 16:08:25', '2018-12-27 07:39:12', 61, 0, ''),
(406, '', 0, '实例', NULL, '', '<p><span style="color: rgb(178, 34, 34);">合并canvas：</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-----------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">var c1=document.getElementById(&quot;c1&quot;);&nbsp;...<br />\r\nvar c2=document.getElementById(&quot;c2&quot;);&nbsp;...<br />\r\nvar rs=document.getElementById(&quot;rs&quot;);<br />\r\nvar context=rs.getContext(&quot;2d&quot;);<br />\r\ncontext.drawImage(c1, 0, 0);<br />\r\ncontext.drawImage(c2, 100, 100);</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:#B22222;">圆型图片</span>：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-----------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>var myHead=document.getElementById(&quot;myHead&quot;);<br />\r\n&nbsp; var ctx2=myHead.getContext(&quot;2d&quot;);<br />\r\n&nbsp; var img2 = new Image();<br />\r\n&nbsp; img2.src = &#39;../images/head.jpg&#39;;<br />\r\n&nbsp; img2.onload = function () {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; var pattern = ctx2.createPattern(img2, &quot;no-repeat&quot;);<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; ctx2.fillStyle=pattern;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; ctx2.arc(34,34,32,0,Math.PI*2,true);<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; ctx2.fill();</p>\r\n\r\n<p>---------------------加边线----<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; ctx2.beginPath();<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; ctx2.arc(34,34,33,0,2*Math.PI);<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; ctx2.strokeStyle=&quot;#fff&quot;;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; ctx2.lineWidth = 2;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; ctx2.stroke();</p>\r\n\r\n<p>}</p>\r\n', '2018-12-02 04:17:41', '2018-12-26 09:50:18', 104, 0, ''),
(407, '', 0, 'Number - 数字对象', NULL, '', '<p>属性：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">constructor</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">MAX_VALUE</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">MIN_VALUE</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">NEGATIVE_INFINITY<span style="white-space:pre"> </span>负无穷大</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">NaN<span style="white-space:pre"> </span>非数字</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">POSITIVE_INFINITY<span style="white-space:pre"> </span>正无穷大</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">prototype</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>方法：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">toExponential(x)<span style="white-space:pre"> </span>把对象的值转换为指数计数法。</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">toFixed(x)</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">toPrecision(x)<span style="white-space:pre"> </span>把数字格式化为指定的长度。</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">toString()</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">valueOf()</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>静态方法：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Number.isFinite() -<br />\r\nNumber.isNaN()&nbsp;-<br />\r\nNumber.parseInt()&nbsp;-<br />\r\nNumber.parseFloat()&nbsp;-<br />\r\nNumber.isInteger()&nbsp;-<br />\r\nNumber.EPSILON&nbsp;-<br />\r\nNumber.isSafeInteger() -</div>\r\n', '2018-12-02 04:26:04', '2018-12-27 05:47:06', 105, 0, '');
