(504, '', 0, '纯函数', NULL, '', '<p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/c_kite/article/details/79138814" target="_blank">https://blog.csdn.net/c_kite/article/details/79138814</a></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>函数的返回结果只依赖于它的参数。</li>\r\n	<li>函数执行过程里面没有副作用。(函数内不会修改参数的属性？)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2019-03-28 09:56:10', '2019-03-28 09:56:02', 35, 0, ''),
(505, '', 0, '入门', NULL, '', '<p>文档：<a href="https://cn.rx.js.org/manual/overview.html" target="_blank">https://cn.rx.js.org/manual/overview.html</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>理解：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/tarena/p/8473993.html">https://www.cnblogs.com/tarena/p/8473993.html</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>视频教程：<a href="https://www.imooc.com/video/13640" target="_blank">https://www.imooc.com/video/13640</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rxjs 理解：解决异步和事件组合的问题</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>cdn:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&lt;script src=&quot;https://cdn.bootcss.com/rxjs/6.0.0-alpha.3/Rx.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>参考：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>创建数据流：<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/98a34189cddd">https://www.jianshu.com/p/98a34189cddd</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>调度器：<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/5624c8a6bd2b">https://www.jianshu.com/p/5624c8a6bd2b</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>// 宏任务 &amp; 微任务</p>\r\n', '2019-03-28 08:24:01', '2019-08-08 03:28:58', 40, 0, ''),
(506, '', 0, '自定义设置', NULL, '', '<p>自定义设置 ： 首选项 -》 设置-用户</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">tab健为4个空格:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&quot;tab_size&quot;: 4,</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">排除指定文件或文件夹：<br />\r\n&quot;folder_exclude_patterns&quot;: [&quot;.svn&quot;, &quot;.git&quot;, &quot;.hg&quot;, &quot;CVS&quot;, &quot;node_modules&quot;]<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2019-03-29 02:41:11', '2019-03-29 02:42:37', 30, 0, ''),
(507, '', 14, 'PCI项目学习笔记', NULL, '', '<p>* es5-shim 和 es5-sham 为了兼容ie8及以下版本</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* vue.use() - 自定义插件 install 方法</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* webpack.ProvidePlugin 不用import直接使用</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*&nbsp;vue+element-ui使用babel-plugin-component按需加载组件及自定义主题对应的scss样式</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* i18n （internationalization的首末字符i和n，18为中间的字符数，国际化的简称）可做中英文切换</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* normalize.css - CSS reset的替代方案</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Jenkins</p>\r\n\r\n<p>用于自动化部署</p>\r\n\r\n<p>是一个开源软件项目，是基于Java开发的一种持续集成工具，用于监控持续重复的工作<br />\r\n功能包括：<br />\r\n1、持续的软件版本发布/测试项目<br />\r\n2、监控外部调用执行的工作</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* qs插件 是一个增加了一些安全性的查询字符串解析和序列化字符串的库<br />\r\n// qs.parse()是将URL解析成对象的形式<br />\r\n// qs.stringify()是将对象 序列化成URL的形式，以&amp;进行拼接</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* suntekmap.js - require.js ?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* polyfill - classList.js , blob , form-data</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>element-ui：<a href="http://element-cn.eleme.io/#/zh-CN" target="_blank">http://element-cn.eleme.io/#/zh-CN</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2019-03-29 02:44:27', '2019-03-30 01:52:47', 19, 0, ''),
(508, '', 0, 'Webstrom', NULL, '', '<p><br />\r\n安装：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/newbie_907486852/article/details/83060282" target="_blank">https://blog.csdn.net/newbie_907486852/article/details/83060282</a> （不要看破解的部分）</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n激活：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/hdp134793/article/details/81530472" target="_blank">https://blog.csdn.net/hdp134793/article/details/81530472</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>汉化：<a href="http://www.smzy.com/smzy/down432513.html" target="_blank">http://www.smzy.com/smzy/down432513.html</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 下载Webstorm2019中文补丁<br />\r\n- 解压后将resources_cn.jar文件复制.Webstormlib目录。<br />\r\n- 汉化完毕，重新打开Webstorm就可以显示中文</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>最终激活：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n<style type="text/css">p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 19.0px; font: 13.0px ''Helvetica Neue''; color: #00a2ff}\r\np.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 19.0px; font: 13.0px ''Helvetica Neue''}\r\nspan.s1 {color: #000000}\r\n</style>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">激活码201812242---提取链接：<a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1WXiQhp8ZSEaH9FD7FiS0Lg">https://pan.baidu.com/s/1WXiQhp8ZSEaH9FD7FiS0Lg</a> </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="p2">提取码：rxv2</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="p2">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>常用设置步骤：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-- 快捷键设置</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- ctrl + w ：选择光标所在的词</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-- 忽略目录node_modules：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">设置-》编辑器-》文件类型(File Types)-》忽略文件和文件夹后面添加;node_modules</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>代码格式化：（缩进等）</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- mac 下 webstorm 格式化代码的快捷键 Option+Command+l<br />\r\n- windows 下 webstorm 格式化代码的快键键 Ctrl+Alt+l</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- centOS 下webstorm 格式化代码的快捷键 Ctrl+Shift+l</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>git配置 &amp; 风格配置：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/zxyun/p/4744744.html">https://www.cnblogs.com/zxyun/p/4744744.html</a></p>\r\n', '2019-03-29 05:43:36', '2019-08-18 07:51:51', 107, 0, ''),
(509, '', 0, 'BEM', NULL, '', '<p>BEM - Block Element Modfier（块元素编辑器）<br />\r\n它可以帮助你创建出可以复用的前端组件和前端代码</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n它有如下3个特性：<br />\r\n易用性 如果想使用BEM，你只需要采用BEM命名规范即可<br />\r\n单元性 独立的块和CSS选择器，可以使得你的代码可重用和单元化<br />\r\n灵活性 使用BEM之后，方法和工具可以按照你喜欢的方式去组织和配置</p>\r\n', '2019-03-29 08:31:41', '2019-03-29 08:31:30', 35, 0, ''),
(510, '', 0, '常用CDN', NULL, '', '<div><span style="color:#FF0000;">vue：</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&lt;script src=&quot;https://cdn.bootcss.com/vue/2.6.10/vue.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="color:#FF0000;">element-ui：</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;https://unpkg.com/element-ui/lib/theme-chalk/index.css&quot;&gt;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&lt;script src=&quot;https://unpkg.com/element-ui/lib/index.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="color:#FF0000;">JQuery：</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&lt;script src=&quot;https://cdn.bootcss.com/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&lt;script src=&quot;https://cdn.bootcss.com/jquery/1.12.1/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</div>\r\n', '2019-03-30 02:12:38', '2019-03-30 05:45:54', 47, 0, ''),
(511, '', 0, '入门', NULL, '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>中文文档：<a href="https://echarts.baidu.com/" target="_blank">https://echarts.baidu.com/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>配置：<a href="https://echarts.apache.org/zh/option.html#title">https://echarts.apache.org/zh/option.html#title</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>基于Echarts插件的多维数据可视化设计和实现：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>（1）<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/mulumeng981/article/details/77848644?utm_source=blogxgwz9" target="_blank">https://blog.csdn.net/mulumeng981/article/details/77848644?utm_source=blogxgwz9</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>（2）<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/mulumeng981/article/details/77862770?tdsourcetag=s_pcqq_aiomsg" target="_blank">https://blog.csdn.net/mulumeng981/article/details/77862770?tdsourcetag=s_pcqq_aiomsg</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>（3）<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/mulumeng981/article/details/77920314?tdsourcetag=s_pcqq_aiomsg" target="_blank">https://blog.csdn.net/mulumeng981/article/details/77920314?tdsourcetag=s_pcqq_aiomsg</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2019-03-30 06:41:33', '2019-07-31 08:10:50', 41, 0, ''),
(512, '', 0, '新', NULL, '', '<p>图片自适应：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>img:<br />\r\nmax-width: 100%;<br />\r\nmax-height: 100%;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>父级：<br />\r\nline-height<br />\r\ntext-align: center;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n容器自适应：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-------------------------------------<br />\r\nposition: absolute;<br />\r\ntop: 40px; // 同级需要减掉的高度<br />\r\nleft: 8px; // 边距<br />\r\nright: 8px;<br />\r\nbottom: 8px;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸 百分比&amp;数值计算：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>height: calc(100% - 10px);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>button状态的css设置：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>有四种状态</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 普通状态<br />\r\n2. hover 鼠标悬停状态<br />\r\n3. active 点击状态<br />\r\n4. focus 取得焦点状态</p>\r\n\r\n<p>.btn:focus{outline:0;} 可以去除按钮或a标签点击后的蓝色边框</p>\r\n', '2019-04-25 07:40:02', '2019-07-25 05:30:04', 55, 0, ''),
(514, '', 0, '防抖', NULL, '', '<p>var text = document.getElementById(&#39;write&#39;);<br />\r\nfunction denounce(fn,delay) {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; var timer;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; return function () {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; if(timer){<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; clearTimeout(timer);<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; timer = setTimeout(function () {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; fn();<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; },delay)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; }<br />\r\n}<br />\r\nfunction write(){<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; console.log(text.value);<br />\r\n}<br />\r\ntext.addEventListener(&#39;input&#39;,denounce(write,1000))</p>\r\n', '2019-05-31 03:28:53', '2019-05-31 03:51:31', 59, 0, ''),
(516, '', 0, '# 输入框+下拉框', NULL, '', '<pre style="background-color:#131314;color:#ebebeb;font-family:''Source Code Pro'';font-size:10.5pt;">\r\n<span style="color:#ed864a;">&lt;el-select </span><span style="color:#ffffff;">v-model</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">=&quot;</span><span style="color:#ffffff;">data</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">.</span><span style="color:#ed94ff;">value</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">&quot; </span><span style="color:#ffffff;">value</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">=&quot;&quot; </span><span style="color:#ffffff;">@change</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">=&quot;selectChange(</span><span style="color:#ffffff;">data</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">)&quot;</span><span style="color:#ed864a;">&gt;\r\n</span><span style="color:#ed864a;">    &lt;el-option </span><span style="color:#ffffff;">v-for</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">=&quot;(</span><span style="color:#ffffff;">item</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">, </span><span style="color:#ffffff;">i</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">) in </span><span style="color:#ed94ff;">items</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">&quot; </span><span style="color:#ffffff;">:key</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">=&quot;</span><span style="color:#ffffff;">i</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">&quot; </span><span style="color:#ffffff;">:label</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">=&quot;</span><span style="color:#ffffff;">item</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">.</span><span style="color:#ed94ff;">name</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">&quot; </span><span style="color:#ffffff;">:value</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">=&quot;</span><span style="color:#ffffff;">item</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">.</span><span style="color:#ed94ff;">key</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">&quot;</span><span style="color:#ed864a;">&gt;&lt;/el-option&gt;\r\n</span><span style="color:#ed864a;">&lt;/el-select&gt;\r\n</span><span style="color:#ed864a;">&lt;el-input </span><span style="color:#ffffff;">v-model</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">=&quot;</span><span style="color:#ffffff;">data</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">.</span><span style="color:#ed94ff;">label</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">&quot; </span><span style="color:#ffffff;">@change</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">=&quot;inputChange(</span><span style="color:#ffffff;">data</span><span style="color:#54b33e;">)&quot;</span><span style="color:#ed864a;">&gt;\r\n</span><span style="color:#ed864a;">&lt;/el-input&gt;\r\n</span>\r\nselectChange (data) {\r\n    this.items.map(x =&gt; {\r\n        if (x.key === data.value) {\r\n            x.label = x.name;\r\n            data.rs = x;\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n}\r\ninputChange (data) {\r\n   data.rs = data.label;\r\n}</pre>\r\n', '2019-06-19 03:33:50', '2019-06-19 03:33:54', 50, 0, ''),
(517, '', 0, 'canvas虚拟画布', NULL, '', '<pre>\r\nvar canvas = d3.create(&#39;canvas&#39;)\r\n    .attr(&#39;width&#39;, 500)\r\n    .attr(&#39;height&#39;, 500);\r\nvar ctx = canvas.node().getContext(&#39;2d&#39;);\r\nctx.rect(20,20,150,100);\r\nctx.stroke();\r\nvar div = d3.select(document.getElementById(&#39;div&#39;))\r\n    .style(&#39;width&#39;, &#39;500px&#39;)\r\n    .style(&#39;height&#39;, &#39;500px&#39;)\r\n    .append(&#39;canvas&#39;)\r\n    .attr(&#39;width&#39;, 500)\r\n    .attr(&#39;height&#39;, 500);\r\nvar ctx2 = div.node().getContext(&#39;2d&#39;);\r\nctx2.drawImage(canvas.node(), 0, 0);</pre>\r\n', '2019-07-02 03:35:47', '2019-07-02 03:35:46', 37, 0, ''),
(518, '', 0, '相关的报错', NULL, '', '<p><span style="color:#FF0000;">Refused to display &#39;http://172.25.21.34:30883/das/help&#39; in a frame because it set &#39;X-Frame-Options&#39; to &#39;deny&#39;.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>解决方法：<a href="https://www.2cto.com/kf/201803/731842.html">https://www.2cto.com/kf/201803/731842.html</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>响应头里修改</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Spring-Security 默认是设置了这个 &ldquo;X-Frame-Options&rdquo; 属性为DENY，把他设置为SAMEORIGIN<br />\r\n解决：在http配置中设置<br />\r\n&lt;http auto-config=&quot;true&quot; use-expressions=&quot;true&quot;&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;headers&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;frame-options policy=&quot;SAMEORIGIN&quot;&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/frame-options&gt;&lt;/headers&gt;<br />\r\n&lt;/http&gt;</p>\r\n', '2019-07-12 02:29:16', '2019-07-12 03:24:24', 71, 0, ''),
(519, '', 0, 'PM2', NULL, '', '<p>PM2是node进程管理工具,可以利用它来简化很多node应用管理的繁琐任务,如性能监控、自动重启、负载均衡等<br />\r\n简介：<a href="https://juejin.im/post/5be406705188256dbb5176f9" target="_blank">https://juejin.im/post/5be406705188256dbb5176f9</a></p>\r\n', '2019-07-12 03:15:41', '2019-07-12 03:15:31', 21, 0, ''),
(520, '', 0, '杂', NULL, '', '<p>Linux的软连接：类似于windows的快捷方式</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ln -s httpd.conf confighttp<br />\r\n输入 confighttp 即代替执行 httpd.conf</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ln -s /opt/node/node-v10.15.3-linux-x64/bin/npm&nbsp; /usr/sbin<br />\r\n之后就能直接用npm执行npm命令</p>\r\n', '2019-07-12 03:21:04', '2019-07-12 03:20:54', 38, 0, ''),
(521, '', 0, '反向代理 http-proxy-middleware', NULL, '', '<pre style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important;">\r\n<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5 !important;">var</span> express = require(&#39;express&#39;<span style="line-height: 1.5 !important;">);\r\n</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5 !important;">var</span> proxy = require(&#39;<span style="color:#FF0000;">http-proxy-middleware</span>&#39;<span style="line-height: 1.5 !important;">);</span>\r\n<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5 !important;">var</span> app =<span style="line-height: 1.5 !important;"> express();</span>\r\napp.use(&#39;/api1&#39;, proxy({target: &#39;http://10.10.10.10:81&#39;, changeOrigin: <span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5 !important;">true</span><span style="line-height: 1.5 !important;">}));\r\n</span></pre>\r\n\r\n<pre style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important;">\r\napp.use(&#39;/api2&#39;, proxy({target: &#39;http://10.10.10.10:82&#39;, changeOrigin: <span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5 !important;">true</span><span style="line-height: 1.5 !important;">}));</span></pre>\r\n\r\n<pre style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important;">\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5 !important;">\r\n</span>app.listen(3000);</pre>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>中文参考：<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/a248b146c55a">https://www.jianshu.com/p/a248b146c55a</a></p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n文档：<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5 !important;"> </span><a href="http://npm.taobao.org/package/http-proxy-middleware#http-proxy-middleware-options" target="_blank">http://npm.taobao.org/package/http-proxy-middleware#http-proxy-middleware-options</a></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<pre class="hljs php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 15px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.42857; overflow-wrap: normal; color: rgb(171, 178, 191); background: rgb(40, 44, 52); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px; white-space: pre; word-break: break-word !important;">\r\n<code class="php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; color: inherit; background-color: transparent; border-radius: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="hljs-keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(198, 120, 221);">var</span> options = {\r\n        target: <span class="hljs-string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);">&#39;http://www.example.org&#39;</span>, <span class="hljs-comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(146, 146, 146);">// 目标服务器 host</span>\r\n        changeOrigin: <span class="hljs-keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(198, 120, 221);">true</span>,               <span class="hljs-comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(146, 146, 146);">// 默认false，是否需要改变原始主机头为目标URL</span>\r\n        ws: <span class="hljs-keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(198, 120, 221);">true</span>,                         <span class="hljs-comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(146, 146, 146);">// 是否代理websockets</span>\r\n        pathRewrite: {\r\n            <span class="hljs-string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);">&#39;^/api/old-path&#39;</span> : <span class="hljs-string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);">&#39;/api/new-path&#39;</span>,     <span class="hljs-comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(146, 146, 146);">// 重写请求，比如我们源访问的是api/old-path，那么请求会被解析为/api/new-path</span>\r\n            <span class="hljs-string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);">&#39;^/api/remove/path&#39;</span> : <span class="hljs-string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);">&#39;/path&#39;</span>           <span class="hljs-comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(146, 146, 146);">// 同上</span>\r\n        },\r\n        router: {\r\n            <span class="hljs-comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(146, 146, 146);">// 如果请求主机 == &#39;dev.localhost:3000&#39;,</span>\r\n            <span class="hljs-comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(146, 146, 146);">// 重写目标服务器 &#39;http://www.example.org&#39; 为 &#39;http://localhost:8000&#39;</span>\r\n            <span class="hljs-string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);">&#39;dev.localhost:3000&#39;</span> : <span class="hljs-string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);">&#39;http://localhost:8000&#39;</span>\r\n        }\r\n    };</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\npathRewrite: {\r\n    &#39;^/das&#39;: &#39;das&#39;\r\n},</pre>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\nheaders: {\r\n    &#39;APP_KEY&#39;: &#39;A21C-H8KU-7NM2-26MG&#39;\r\n},</pre>\r\n\r\n<p>onProxyRes(proxyRes, req, res) {&nbsp;//监听proxy的回应事件</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">console.log(proxyRes, req, res);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:#FF0000;">changeOrigin</span>值设置说明：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>如果后端服务托管在虚拟主机的时候，也就是一个IP对应多个域名，需要通过域名区分服务，那么参数changeOrigin必须为true(默认为false)，这样才会传递给后端正确的Host头，虚拟主机才能正确回应。否则http-proxy-middleware会原封不动将本地HTTP请求发往后端，包括Host: localhost而不是Host: httpbin.org，只有正确的Host才能使用虚拟主机，不然会返回404 Not Found</p>\r\n', '2019-07-12 09:31:04', '2019-08-05 02:43:20', 21, 0, ''),
