(540, '', 0, '报错', NULL, '', '<p>git 推送时报：<br />\r\nremote: invalid credentials<br />\r\nfatal: Authentication failed for &#39;http://xxxxx&#39;<br />\r\n原因：上一次推送输账号密码时输入错误<br />\r\n解决：<br />\r\n控制面板用户帐户凭据管理器<br />\r\n找到输错账户密码的点开删掉，重新推送时会提示重新输入</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>推送时报：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Updates were rejected because a pushed branch tip is behind its remote ...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>原因：自己当前版本低于远程仓库版本</p>\r\n\r\n<p>解决：git pull origin master</p>\r\n\r\n<p>先拉取最新的再重新推送</p>\r\n\r\n<p><font color="#2f2f2f" face="-apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">参考：</span></font><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/004f47f908c5">https://www.jianshu.com/p/004f47f908c5</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>以下未处理：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>报错：... HttpRequestException encountered ...&nbsp;returned error: 403 ...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>// 原因：Github 禁用了TLS v1.0 and v1.1，必须<span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">更新Windows的git凭证管理器</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>// 解决：<a href="https://github.com/Microsoft/Git-Credential-Manager-for-Windows/releases/" target="_blank">https://github.com/Microsoft/Git-Credential-Manager-for-Windows/releases/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>进入上面链接，点第一个如GCMW-1.16.0.exe</p>\r\n\r\n<p>下载之后 重新提交（当时是删掉原来的重新克隆重新提交，弹窗登录github就好了）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>git合并时因<span style="color:#FF0000;">eslint校验报错</span>不能合并，命令后加--no-verify跳过验证就好了</p>\r\n', '2019-07-25 12:34:10', '2019-08-14 11:14:33', 106, 0, ''),
