(604, '', 0, '入门', NULL, '', '<p>1、关闭Jenkins<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;只需要在访问jenkins服务器的网址url地址后加上exit。例如我jenkins的地址http://localhost:8080/，那么我只需要在浏览器地址栏上敲下http://localhost:8080/exit 网址就能关闭jenkins服务.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br />\r\n2、重启Jenkies<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; http://localhost:8080/restart</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3、重新加载配置信息</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; http://localhost:8080/reload</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>系统管理：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_42713970/article/details/88556455">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_42713970/article/details/88556455</a></p>\r\n', '2019-08-19 05:40:39', '2019-08-19 05:50:04', 125, 0, ''),
