(608, '', 0, '经验记录', NULL, '', '<p>-- 安装时会默认安装一些插件，报网络问题，跳过安装了（提示还可以设置代理）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-- 手动安装插件：<span style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: nowrap;">&nbsp;</span>Manage Jenkins -》 Manage Plugins -&gt; Available，搜索要安装的插件，点击安装</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-- 安装插件过程中一直卡死在第一个插件(<span style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;">Oracle Java SE Development Kit&nbsp;</span>)上</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-- url后加/restart 重启报：Jenkins cannot restart itself as currently configured.</p>\r\n', '2019-08-19 06:08:18', '2019-08-19 06:10:21', 125, 0, ''),
(609, '', 0, '后羿采集器', NULL, '', '<p>官网：<a href="http://www.houyicaiji.com/">http://www.houyicaiji.com/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>教程：<a href="http://www.houyicaiji.com/?type=post&amp;pid=1001">http://www.houyicaiji.com/?type=post&amp;pid=1001</a></p>\r\n', '2019-08-19 13:54:40', '2019-08-19 13:54:39', 111, 0, ''),
(610, '', 0, '遍历', NULL, '', '<p>多层数组嵌套获取最内层中数组里对象的值</p>\r\n\r\n<p>----------------------------<br />\r\n&nbsp;arr=[[[[{id:11}]]]]<br />\r\nwhile(Array.isArray(arr)) {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; arr = arr[0]<br />\r\n}<br />\r\nconsole.log(arr.id)</p>\r\n', '2019-08-23 06:52:51', '2019-08-23 06:52:41', 126, 0, ''),
(611, '', 0, 'Mac - npm', NULL, '', '<p><span style="color:#FF0000;">淘宝镜像安装</span>：sudo npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org --verbose</p>\r\n\r\n<p>安装完后 <span style="color:#FF0000;">sudo </span>cnpm install</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:#FF0000;">终端走代理</span>：export http_proxy=http://proxyAddress:port</p>\r\n\r\n<p>参考：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/u011537073/article/details/71125571">https://blog.csdn.net/u011537073/article/details/71125571</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>其他：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>rm -rf node_modules<br />\r\nrm package-lock.json<br />\r\nnpm cache clear --force</p>\r\n', '2019-08-25 00:57:58', '2019-08-25 01:15:10', 109, 0, ''),
(612, '', 0, 'RESTful', NULL, '', '<pre style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important;">\r\n<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5 !important;">POST表示创建资源，PUT表示更新资源.但实际上两者都可以用来创建或是更新数据.单从技术上来说,他们并没有什么区别.但是在HTTP规范中POST是非等幂的,多次调用会产生不同的结果,\r\n　　比如:创建一个用户,由于网络原因或是其他原因多创建了几次,那么将会有多个用户被创建.而PUT id</span>/<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5 !important;">456则会创建一个id为456的用户,多次调用还是会创建的结果是一样的,所以PUT是等幂的.</span></pre>\r\n', '2019-08-29 11:07:02', '2019-08-29 11:06:54', 68, 0, ''),
(613, '', 0, '文件导入导出', NULL, '', '<p>导入：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-----------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&lt;input type=&quot;file&quot; @change=&quot;upload&quot; /&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>let file = event.target.files[0];<br />\r\nlet reg = /^application/(x-tar|x-gzip)$/;<br />\r\nif(!reg.test(file.type)) {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; this.$message({<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; type: &#39;warning&#39;,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; message: &#39;仅支持上传.tar或者.gz文件&#39;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; });<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; return false;<br />\r\n}<br />\r\nlet formData = new FormData();<br />\r\nformData.append(&#39;file&#39;, file);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>let url = &#39;/das/service/manage/model/upload&#39;,<br />\r\nheaders = {&#39;Content-Type&#39;: &#39;multipart/form-data&#39;};<br />\r\nAxios.post(url, formData, { headers }).then(({ data }) =&gt; {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; return data;<br />\r\n});</p>\r\n\r\n<p>// 关联：<a href="http://notebook3.com/__it/index.php?act=searchAll&amp;kw=formData">http://notebook3.com/__it/index.php?act=searchAll&amp;kw=formData</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>导出：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-----------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>let link = document.createElement(&#39;a&#39;);<br />\r\nlet url = &#39;/download?reqParam=&#39; + encodeURIComponent(`{ids:[${id}]}`);<br />\r\nlink.href = url;<br />\r\nlink.click();<br />\r\nlink = null;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2019-08-30 13:28:31', '2019-08-31 03:49:51', 127, 0, ''),
(614, '', 0, 'VSCode', NULL, '', '<p>官网：<a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/">https://code.visualstudio.com/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>中文文档：<a href="https://jeasonstudio.gitbooks.io/vscode-cn-doc/content/">https://jeasonstudio.gitbooks.io/vscode-cn-doc/content/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>视频教程：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/hp1025/article/details/86147335">https://blog.csdn.net/hp1025/article/details/86147335</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>汉化：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-----------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>左边栏的 Extensions -》搜 Chinese Language -》安装中文(简体) -》安装完后重启</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>快捷键：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-----------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>文件 -》首选项 -》键盘快捷方式</p>\r\n\r\n<p>找到 向下复制行 -》改成 Shift + Ctrl + D</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>缩进设置：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-----------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>文件 -》首选项 -》设置</p>\r\n\r\n<p>搜 tab size,&nbsp; 改成2 或 4</p>\r\n\r\n<p>搜&nbsp;detectIndentation, 关闭自动监测的功能</p>\r\n', '2019-08-31 09:44:55', '2019-09-19 06:18:23', 107, 0, ''),
